**Learning:** In complex views (like the vault search in `HistoryPage.tsx`), rendering an inline anonymous component inside an array `.map()` triggers full unmount/re-render cycles for *all* items whenever a single item changes (e.g. toggling a bookmark). This O(N) re-render behavior severely bottlenecks UI thread performance as the list size grows.
